Feel very much better today those pills seem to have done me the world of good.
15th . Pretty busy today for I am Batt. Orderly Sergt, in a camp there are so many things for one to look after. Had another meeting of the Sergts last night the Mess is to be opened tonight a good job too Most of the boys were pretty full last night.
Heavy frost this morning but the sun is struggling to show itself for a while hope he gets out
Very heavy sick parade some of them with nothing at all the matter with them at the present time we have a terrible lot of malingerers